review:
好有趣的休闲弹球游戏，小瓢虫很可爱！
不过也太冷门了，正经攻略都找不着，虽然不影响通关;










顺便吐槽下结局蚊子真丑……

Pros:
- Vivid and creative design;
- Outstanding and catchy soundtrack;
- Challenging levels, CRAZY bosses;
- Precise and intuitive controls;
- Charismatic characters, lively world;
- Good sidequests;

Cons: 
- A bug almost blocked me from finishing the main story, had to exploit some glitch to "jump ahead" and go through an impassable area. Forums have pointed the bug since launch and nothing was done up till now, November;
- Somewhat short (100% completed in under 12 hours);
- Some moves and goals are not very clear. Sometimes I would look up on the web how to reach something and I was more than one time surprised like "oh, I can do that? I never knew";
- Some upgrades are very, very stupid and unnecessary. It's much better to open chests with actual game-changing items;
- Very addictive, specially for metroidvania fans;

Final rating: 9/10
I sure hope this game gets enough attention to get a sequel. Hopefully with a co-op mode!!
